{"tid":721757,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony 籌備肥西女超級英雄電影Faith","createTime":"2018-06-29T02:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T06:11:36.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"facee80918b3e2e948d26f20314275e3c7056373","tid":721757,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"Deadline報導，SONY正在發展Valiant出版社（勇士）的Faith個人電影。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\nFaith是位極度宅女，超愛Dr. Who和Sherlock，還是龍與地下城桌遊的超級粉絲！<br />\n他也有著社會新鮮人都有的煩惱，戀愛、工作、雙重身分等等，<br />\n但他也十分樂觀開朗，是團隊中的燈塔，在讀他的作品時是滿開心的，很多宅哏，<br />\n也有滿多笑料，也有不少女權議題，但不會刻意描寫，或矯枉過正的情況。<br />\n（雖然當年有幫希拉蕊站台XD）<br />\n　　<br />\n她在勇士宇宙中是名靈能者（Pisot），可以想像成是漫威的變種人，<br />\n擁有飛行能力和操控能量力場（可以帶人一起飛或隔空取物之類的），<br />\n英雄代號為「和風」（Zyphyr）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而另一部SONY確定開拍的勇士作品為馮迪索主演的Bloodshot個人電影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qKGAy5Il.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqKGAy5Il.jpg&h=f4f4bcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jCUzwUTl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjCUzwUTl.jpg&h=32c5909e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38f67661f2761e52d80362e853466be7f93ec2be","tid":721757,"uid":182286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"048daae5387a58d1af7da5a4ddc4745a8affddf1","tid":721757,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會睇<br />\n應該好笑"},{"pid":"6007c1939b39fd46bb135017c6c31dfcc2542a0e","tid":721757,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"還完度好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec02567090de4a8736a670